程序包 projecttwo

类 TestBed

java.lang.Object
projecttwo.TestBed
public class TestBed extends Object
The TestBed is for test uses. It implements the functionality of testing the Member class's compareTo() method and testing the Date's class isValid() method. The TestBed class and the TestBed object should only appear at the Date class's main method and Member class's main method.
作者:
Kangwei Zhu Michael ISRAEL

  • 方法详细资料

    • testMemberCompareTo

      public int testMemberCompareTo(Member testCandidateOne, Member testCandidateTwo, int testCaseNum, int expectedValue)
      This method is for testing the Member class's compareTo() method. It will compare the expected output with the output that the current compareTo method will produce.
      参数:
      testCandidateOne - The first member object.
      testCandidateTwo - The second member object.
      testCaseNum - The number of current test case.
      expectedValue - The result what you expect firstMember.compareTo(secondMember) will return.
      返回:
      Return 1 if the expected output is the same as what compareTo() method returns. Return 0 otherwise.

    • testDateIsValid

      public int testDateIsValid(Date testCandidate, int testCaseNum, boolean expectedValue)
      This method is for testing the Date class's isValid() method. It will compare the expected value of isValid() that should return with the value isValid() is actually returning.
      参数:
      testCandidate - The Date object that are going to be tested
      testCaseNum - The number of current test case
      expectedValue - The value what you expect Date.isValid() will produce.
      返回:
      if the expected output is the same as what isValid() method returns, then return 1. Return 0 otherwise.
